    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793549_8_6163-6246",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6163-6246",
      "markText": "至道安始唱出家应无姓之说，返大圣释迦之本，单号释道安；后获《增一阿含经》，诵“四河入海，无复河名。四姓为沙门，皆称释种”文句，遂则而效之，永以为例。僧之无姓，自此始。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793549&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6163&rangeEnd=6246",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/986325a071c69d0d9865e1b?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6163&rangeEnd=6246"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "29793549_11_7410-7450",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "7410-7450",
      "markText": "自古道佛二教冲突，佛教所受厄难最大者，我国佛教史上，凡四见焉：谓之三武一宗之难。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=29793549&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7410&rangeEnd=7450",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/986325a071c69d0d9865e1b?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7410&rangeEnd=7450"
    },
    {
